text: Ella Gibbons (born 24 November 1994) is a Scottish netball player. She was selected to represent the Scotland netball team at the 2019 Netball World Cup. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Scottish netball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:2019 Netball World Cup players Category:Loughborough Lightning netball players Category:Netball Superleague players Category:Sirens Netball players
